{"type": "article", "id": 28720, "title": "可调节的儿童单车", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-27T06:51:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121023lk1c7dBy92xmgUtG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>孩子成长的速度总是令人始料未及，不管是衣服还是玩具都很容易处于不断更新换代的状态。为了不让小小的单车最后只能落得在角落蒙灰的命运，设计师 Zhang Ting 推出了一款可以调节的儿童单车。最开始，单车的座椅和把手都被设置在最低高度，也没有动力传动系统，依靠孩子自己滑步前行。在这个过程中，孩子可以锻炼自己的平衡能力。等孩子长大后，底部的单条链结构可以很轻松地连接起车架和后轮毂，就变成了一辆真正的单车。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121021WpP7OD1wxTlEqoMF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121021qMpjkzDQb1cm2KtL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121022zbDvJR2W5gSXYc0I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121022XbjhVIv3E1zsrD6M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}